{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5436e7689b","title":"中央批准西北局关于开展三反整风运动指示的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"896176ab14","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"5436e7689b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f1198bf13e","type":"title","text":"中央批准西北局关于开展三反整风运动指示的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"bd251de806","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"35c15aaad2","type":"appellation","text":"西北局：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"615679e3c6","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十八日的整风指示稿，已收到，看过，认为是正确的，可即照此施行。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"37c83f881a","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央十二月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"5436e7689b"}],"page":{"id":"f9f468307b","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"5436e7689b","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"b3330d7787","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央西北局1951年12月18日关于开展反对贪污、反对浪费、反对官像主义的整风运动的指示。指示说，西北局决定从现在起，有系统地普遍地发动全党和所有工作人员，向贪污现象、浪费现象和官像主义现象作坚决严肃的斗争。大行政区机关和省、市级机关，现在就应立即动手，集中力量在一个月时间内完成这个运动。各专区和县也要在本月或明年1月开始。各机关、企业、团体，一般地都要先从开展反对贪污和反对浪费斗争入手，由此联系检查领导工作中的官停主义作风，并从而讨论堵塞漏洞，提高工作效率的各项必要办法和制度，最后在这个基础上，引导群众转到增产节约运动中去。正在进行整党工作的机关，应把这个反对贪污、反对浪费、反对官像主义的整风和整党结合起来，首先解决那些贪污、浪费、官停主义和脱离群众的突出问题，然后进一步进行共产主义教育，以至登记处理等。"}],"contents":[{"id":"24aafaca5b","type":"title","text":"中央批准西北局关于开展三反整风运动指示的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"26c9ad4fff","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"3cf99fd675","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十八日的整风指示稿，已收到，看过，认为是正确的，可即照此施行。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"b3330d7787","type":"paragraph","text":"西北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b"},{"id":"d99c2ac1f6","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b"}],"page":{"id":"5080e0cbe7","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"5436e7689b","start":183,"end":183}}}},"__N_SSG":true}